# Module 2 runs fully offline by default — the test suite uses an in-memory Supabase
# mock that models Row-Level Security. You do NOT need any of the values below to pass CI.
#
# They exist for the OPTIONAL "prove it against a real database" path (see README).
# Create a free Supabase project, run supabase/migrations/0001_meals.sql in its SQL editor,
# then set these and run the app with USE_REAL_SUPABASE=1. Never commit the real values.

# USE_REAL_SUPABASE=1
# SUPABASE_URL=
# SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=
